title: OIP-13: Deposit $1M of excess reserves into Aave
body:
Summary:
Deposit $1M of DAI into Aave, representing 11.489% (2√33 percent) of excess treasury reserves as of 6/30. Benefits include:
 - Yield on excess stablecoin reserves
 - Fostering strategic partnership with Aave
 - Accumulate stkAAVE rewards

Additional context and discussion available on the the OIP-13 forum post:
https://forum.olympusdao.finance/d/44-oip-13-what-of-excess-dai-should-olympus-deposit-into-aave/

Treasury contract to view excess reserves (line 11):
https://etherscan.io/address/0x31f8cc382c9898b273eff4e0b7626a6987c846e8#readContract

For: Deposit $1M of excess reserves into Aave
Against: Do not touch excess reserves
author: 0x26022dAC731Fa8B8181298F20beB827382b8a138
